ansible installation commands

sudo yum update -y
sudo yum install ansible -y

ansible commands

To make connection
ansible -i /home/ec2-user/ansible/inventory.yml servers -m ping --private-key=~/.ssh/ansi_key

To launch playbook
ansible-playbook -i /home/ec2-user/ansible/inventory.yml install_docker.yml

To check installation done
ansible -i /home/ec2-user/ansible/hosts servers -a "docker --version"





